I"Â<p><strong>To activate right-to-left theme orientation</strong> you need to do the following steps:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Log in and go to your <strong>Admin Panel</strong></li>
  <li>Go to <strong>Appearance</strong> &gt; <strong>Theme options</strong></li>
  <li>Set <strong>Content shift right to left</strong> value to <strong>YES</strong></li>
  <li>Press <strong>Update</strong></li>
</ol>

